<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-03 16:10 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, January 3 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Sunday closed at 1526.75 points, down 5.04
points from that of Saturday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 6,879,199 shares exchanged hands in 804 turns and
the turnover stood at 13.61 billion rials (about 2.27 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 21 companies made gains while those of 22 others
declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
