</P>
<P>
He said Muslims cannot even imagine the "devilish act of
shedding the blood of innocent people during the holy month of
Ramadan. But some anti-state elements are carrying out these
nefarious acts to create instability in the country for their
ulterior motives."
</P>
<P>
These "anti-state elements" cannot escape punishment, he said.
</P>
<P>
He said it is the basic obligation of the government to provide
security and protection to the life and property of the citizens.
"We will fully exploit our resources for this purpose," he said.
</P>
</TEXT>
