</P>
<P>
The HSI dropped 236.82 points, or 2.36 percent, to close the
morning session at 9,811.76.
</P>
<P>
The stocks fell 72.86 points, or 0.72 percent, to close the
half-day trade at 10,048.58 Thursday. 
</P>
